       Your victorious ship lands on the Nemesis-3 planet       You exit your ship and make your way towards a large       Towering structure.  Entering through an open       Portal you find yourself in the center of a dark hall       Dimly lit by flickering electric-blue lamps.       Before you is a crystalline lattice containing       Six incredibly radiant jewels, each of different hue.       The lattice prevents you from taking the jewels.